Playwright

What is Playwright ?
	It is an open source tool build by Microsoft that enables reliable end to end UI and API automation testing for modern web apps.
	Highly rated on GitHub
	An out-of-process automation driver that is not limited by the scope of in-page javascript execution
	closer to selenium WebDriver than cypress

What is Playwright Test?
	- Built-in test runner with similar syntax to Jest
	- Ability to run tests in parallel with the ability to enable retries
	- Useful built in reporters with screenshots, videos and trace viewer
	- VS COde extension to help in building and maintaining your tests

Why choose it?
	- The ability to run API/UI regression tests in the same framework
	- The rich feature set that comes built in to Playwright
	- Excellent error handling when tests fail
	- Flexibility provided with project configurations
	- Locators auto-waiting and retry-ability


